# Bottle Waste Detection using YOLO

Final project completed during the IIIT Hyderabad Computer Vision Internship.

Tasks:
- Dataset preparation and annotation using Label Studio
- Image preprocessing using FFmpeg
- YOLO model training and fine-tuning
- Model evaluation using Precision, Recall, and mAP
- Object detection on unseen test images

Technologies:
YOLO, Ultralytics, Label Studio, FFmpeg, Python

Results:
Precision: ~1.00
Recall: ~0.999
mAP@0.5: ~0.995
